### Fluxos - Get All
GET {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/fluxos
Accept: application/json

### Fluxos - Get by ID
GET {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/fluxos/1
Accept: application/json

### Fluxos - Post
POST {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/fluxos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "valorPago": 120.5,
  "consumo": 80,
  "status": 1
}

### Fluxos - Put
PUT {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/fluxos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idFluxo": 1,
  "valorPago": 120.5,
  "consumo": 80,
  "status": 1
}

### Fluxos - Change Status (with body)
PATCH {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/fluxos/status/1
Content-Type: application/json

0

