### Usuarios - Get All
GET {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usuarios
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Usuarios - Get Inativos
GET {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usuarios/inativos
Accept: application/json

### Usuarios - Get by ID
GET {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usuarios/1
Accept: application/json

### Usuarios - Get by CPF
GET {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usuarios/cpf?cpf=12345678901
Accept: application/json

### Usuarios - Post
POST {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Joao Silva",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "situacao": 1,
  "matricula": "MAT001",
  "tipoUsuario": 1,
  "bairro": "Centro"
}

### Usuarios - Put
PUT {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usuarios/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "nome": "Joao Silva",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "situacao": 1,
  "matricula": "MAT001",
  "tipoUsuario": 1,
  "bairro": "Centro"
}

### Usuarios - Change Situacao
PATCH {{Civitas.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usuarios/situacao/1
Accept: application/json

